        <mxCell id="m-map-text" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=11;fontColor=#374151;spacingLeft=20;spacingTop=10;" value="• Coletor de Evento — hooks/useAdaptiveSession.ts (sendEvent) + app/api/session/event/route.ts (POST handler)&#xa;• Normalização — route.ts: valida sessionId/itemId/category; eventType = &quot;view&quot; como default seguro&#xa;• Filtro — useAdaptiveSession.ts: debounce de 300 ms para eventos &quot;view&quot;, evitando flood de scroll&#xa;• Agregação — lib/event-monitor.ts → processClickEvent(): aplica DECAY_FACTOR (0.85) sobre os scores anteriores e soma EVENT_WEIGHTS[type] na categoria atual&#xa;• Gerador de Sintoma — lib/event-monitor.ts: monta SessionStateRecord (categoryScores, lastCategory, lastItemViewed, eventCount, ttl)&#xa;• Alterar Base — lib/session-repository.ts → saveSessionState(): INSERT em session_state (PostgreSQL)&#xa;• Emissor de Sintoma — lib/event-monitor.ts: return AdaptiveResponse — consumido pelo Analisador (lib/adaptation-engine.ts)&#xa;&#xa;Constantes do loop (Knowledge): DECAY_FACTOR=0.85 · SESSION_TTL_SECONDS=1800 · EVENT_WEIGHTS={view:1, click:2, search:3, favorite:4, add_to_cart:5}" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="100" y="920" width="1450" height="200" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
